works.description:
Several stories which are being exchanged
 
on this site are under contract to Omnific Publishing and have been  
published in edited, but substantially similar, form, including:
Boycotts & Barflies ISBN #978-1-936305-00-1 released 2/16/10); I Love LA  
(published as The Unidentified Redhead, ISBN #978-1-936-06-3 released  
2/16/10); Passion Fish (ISBN #978-1-936305-4 released 2/16/10); Cocktails
&  
Dreams (under contract); Stitches and Scars (ISBN #978-1-936305-17-9  
released 5/14/10) and others.
